data.description: If you’re looking for a turn key property look not further!!! This 3 bedroom, 1.5 bathroom home is packed with updates including a brand new kitchen, completely updated bathroom, and all new flooring on the main floor. Downstairs you’ll find an additional 465 sq ft of finishable living space with a half bathroom and access to a 2 car garage. Large newly fenced in back yard with an additional side lot totaling almost a full acre is perfect for entertaining and large gatherings. An newly built additional 1 car detached garage with access to the back yard can be finished and utilized for whatever your heart desires. Located in Maysville Local School District. Sellers are motivated…Call today for your private showing
